mcp_json_config_hint:
MCP設定JSONを貼り付けてください。例:
{
  "context7": {
    "command": "npx",
    "args": [
      "-y",
      "@upstash/context7-mcp@latest"
    ]
  }
}

またはmcpServersラッパー付き:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {...}
  }
}

